FBIS3-58574 "drweu011_o_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 CYPRUS Vorvolakos Appointed National Guard Commander NC1801102194 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in Greek 1000 GMT 18 Jan 94 NC1801102194 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Lieutenant General Nikolaos Vorvolakos has been appointed the new National Guard commander. Government spokesman Ioannis Kasoulidhis announced the appointment following the Council of Ministers meeting this morning. Kasoulidhis said the decision to appoint Vorvolakos was made in consultations involving the governments of Greece and Cyprus.
